  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/12/apple-in-app-purchases-setting-warning-ios7-1/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/db1e89225a7711c6465c98e48c3e2c6a/QQ20140313-1.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/25/apple-in-app-purchases-update/\">儿童误用应用内购</a>的官司已经<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/15/ftc-apple-settlement-in-app-purchases/\">了结</a>，但为了以防万一，苹果在刚刚上线的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/10/apple-releases-ios-7-1/\">iOS 7.1</a> 中加入了一项提警功能。从现在开始，用户在完成内购后会看到「未来 15 分钟内无需再次输入密码便可完成支付」的提示，这样一来，就能让使用者在操作时多长个心眼了。当然，如果你不喜欢这样的话也可以在设定中关闭相关选项，但身边有孩子的朋友，还是将其开启比较保险啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/12/apple-in-app-purchases-setting-warning-ios7-1/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://news.cnet.com/8301-13579_3-57620219-37/ios-7.1-warns-you-about-in-app-purchase-window/\" target=\"_blank\">CNET</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/12/apple-in-app-purchases-setting-warning-ios7-1/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20848568/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/12/apple-in-app-purchases-setting-warning-ios7-1/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
